🍎 E-Learning Platform Redesign – UI/UX & Front-End Development
This project involves redesigning an online learning platform to improve user onboarding, progress tracking, and multimedia content display. Developed during my internship to boost navigation and learner engagement.
🔧 Project Goal
Create an intuitive onboarding experience for new users.
Implement clear progress tracking for courses.
Enhance multimedia content display for a richer learning experience.
✨ Key Features
🎯 User Onboarding – Guided flows to help learners get started quickly.
📊 Progress Tracking – Visual indicators showing course completion and milestones.
🎥 Multimedia Support – Seamless integration of videos, audio, and interactive content.
🧭 Improved Navigation – Simplified menus and pathways for effortless exploration.
🛠 Tools Used
Figma – UI/UX design
📸 Preview
